# PAUSE — Persistent Research Loop

Rename or copy this file to `PAUSE` (no extension) in the same directory as the
filled `RESEARCH-CHARTER.md` to refuse new Brain sessions.

Admin phrase: `pause research loop ⟨pool-id⟩` → create `PAUSE`.  
Resume: remove `PAUSE`, then `start research loop ⟨pool-id⟩`.

Agents must exit immediately when `PAUSE` is present.
`check-research-loop.sh` exits non-zero while paused.
